John,<br>
     Have no new data from the DD Express or other sources. Spent the weekend going to a VVA regional conference, and was inundated with data on everything else but (Jesse Brown's resignation from the VA effective July 1st, for instance).  The Express can be reached through &lt;VET66A@aol.com&gt;  It's quite a mixed bag of material from announcements, SOSs, personal observations, jokes, to who knows what next.<br>
                                                            Know what you mean about kids.  Mine are 24, 23 and 19.  The &quot;old man&quot; here is just getting out of the stupid stage.  At least I no longer embarrass them just by walking out the front door.  My oldest son still considers me too idealistic and naive.  He believes I don't know a lot of the games, just because I refuse to play them.  At any rate, I'm proud of the first charge....Xin Loi.  [there's that &quot;phrase&quot; again, Doc Spatz, or maybe I should go &quot;Philly&quot;: &quot;YO!! Gotta problem widdat?!]  
